Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.74,0:22:41.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}也因有所不同　才更加有趣
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.03,0:22:43.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}舊石器時代　是大前輩
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}從那時起就沒有改變
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}有想要的東西的話
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.38,0:22:49.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes！用這雙手
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.65,0:22:50.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes！現在立刻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}自己來創造！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.41,0:22:58.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}每天的各種奇思妙想
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}加上一點小靈感
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.08,0:23:04.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}輕輕哼著歌
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.14,0:23:08.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}即便不完美也一笑了之
